### Test Query - Get Products with Dynamic Fields
POST http://localhost:5275/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ products { nodes { id data name description price stock category } } }"
}

### Test Query - With Filtering
POST http://localhost:5275/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { products(where: { name: { contains: \"test\" } }) { nodes { id name description price } } }"
}

### Introspection - Check ProductView Type
POST http://localhost:5275/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "{ __type(name: \"ProductView\") { name fields { name type { name kind ofType { name } } } } }"
}
